<template>
  <v-card></v-card>
</template>
<script setup>
import { useRoute } from "vue-router";
import { useStore } from "vuex";
const route = useRoute();
const store = useStore();
const job_id = ref(route.params.job_id);
onMounted(async () => {
  await store.dispatch("triggerSetEstimates", { job_id: job_id });
});
</script>
<style scoped></style>
